snippet.title: "you don't know your Souths!" Niko calls out Adley for getting Lost in 99 NiGHTS
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

Here's a SUPER funny moment from our 99 Nights in the Forest on Roblox video we just posted! Adley was lost and didn't know how to get back to the safety of our campfire so Niko told her it was SOUTH! But Adley said she didn't know her souths! Niko is always the funniest and showed her where the compass is but had to tease here just a little!

enjoy some A for Adley videos: https://www.youtube.com/c/AforAdleyLe...
have a blast with our A for Adley Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMHpfyAqrjrhn-mRS2bUL0g
